{"tid":2048482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 係時候同世界connect","createTime":"2020-06-03T00:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T22:05:16.000Z","uid":29476,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1fcfe119222e818c57435f6dee438833275256","tid":2048482,"uid":29476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T00:26:00.000Z","msg":"其實香港更應值著呢個機會Connect 全世界<br />\n<br />\n首先<br />\n撐George Floyd 唔等於 撐裝修<br />\n對抗警暴 唔等於 極左/無政府主義<br />\n發聲等於對不公平事件表達不滿而connect <br />\nBlack lives matter <br />\n正等於人地為香港人發聲一樣 <br />\nHK lives 係世界各地都有人同你 matter<br />\n不過今次主題係 BLM <br />\n受害嘅係黑人 唔係港人<br />\n人地同我地connect都一樣<br />\n人地幫我地 我地幫翻人<br />\n普世價值相同<br />\n唔好好似MC jin咁選擇性歧視 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先睇下全世界同美國connect: <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xj7ub2G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxj7ub2G.png&h=dcf07b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EeBiPPw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEeBiPPw.png&h=64f79272&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0iK4LnV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0iK4LnV.png&h=50bf44fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3gkWBuF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3gkWBuF.png&h=4bd89b63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wbF29L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wbF29L.png&h=37ecdfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VwbZzgy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwbZzgy.png&h=04634281&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nv7YPP3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnv7YPP3.png&h=d6326abc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/apgR9Qg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FapgR9Qg.png&h=d4fc1a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反警暴唔等於反trump 定唔反trump<br />\n種族歧視 黑警問題<br />\n係美國其中歷史上比較嚴重嘅問題<br />\n有無trump都可以有黑警<br />\n有無trump 都會有種族歧視<br />\ntrump嘅處理手法係點 佢上任點處理 <br />\n就係另外一個話題<br />\n要分清楚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n袁爸爸以佢嘅角度分析得幾好<br />\n以前打日本 德國 蘇聯<br />\n就係要打倒君國/納粹主義 <br />\n要為錢就唔會打佢<br />\n係為有一個更好嘅普世價值世界<br />\n佢同19才子講都一樣就係<br />\n美國佬錯信中國會民主進步<br />\n誤判低估佢哋嘅共產思想<br />\n搞到衣家共和兩黨合作/鬥黃<br />\n呢一個亦係佢地當香港係戰場又好<br />\n當我地係棋子又好嘅原因<br />\n只要勝利 就能寫下歷史<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fYdNvW3lwNY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfYdNvW3lwNY&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=3ec0a053\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fYdNvW3lwNY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然我地都有好多問題<br />\n64都反對通知書<br />\n歡迎大家討論brainstorm 下<br />\n點打 打唔打 呢場波"},{"pid":"8e18801a5da05634f59835efd8b6c4cca291d84e","tid":2048482,"uid":29476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T00:34:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6d6acfc9e28b77fa32532b2399c30a95e0073006","tid":2048482,"uid":29476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T00:46:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc3a995d86042c12acbf75bce3666e36493d344a","tid":2048482,"uid":53105,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T00:49:24.000Z","msg":"反外國警暴，跟住比香港警暴鎮壓，到時真係connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7ddd4dbf9dff75f32d59f02711a453ebf4d0fb","tid":2048482,"uid":33621,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T00:49:47.000Z","msg":"Connect班撚屌有撚用咩，要出聲嗰d一早撐咗<br />\n睇下幾多成年冇出聲/奶共嘅外國左膠post #blackouttuesday先啦<br />\n<br />\n呢個時間真係要小心打，post美國警暴可以，但BLM就算罷啦"},{"pid":"9898b3cc64f6fbb0fe97c13c8e642fe4cfc2ca55","tid":2048482,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T00:53:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NUAdgt5Glk0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNUAdgt5Glk0&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D