仲未connect嗰班好多係唔會理香港<br />\n甚至好多偽善撚<br />\n好多人屌美國政府係因為政治正確, 對香港既事不聞不問亦都係因為咁<br />\n撐我地既人入面有撐Trump (e.g. 共和黨員 / Avi) 亦都有反Trump (e.g. 某D民主黨員)<br />\n無謂做得太盡"},{"pid":"e9a1b5f65d835b77e490bf946f8158ab0f31f11e","tid":2048482,"uid":145928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"antifa is CCP <br />\nfuck the Chinese <br />\nwho heat the street"},{"pid":"ae5eb5803adb84f2393f8b4e550c8e8035d66594","tid":2048482,"uid":29476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:19:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9d618369ba028762e783dc6cb2881b62c385b2ef","tid":2048482,"uid":29476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:41:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b4ab1d22fed9ba3bfab806f2735a108787eae052","tid":2048482,"uid":301880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:58:35.000Z","msg":"其實大家睇睇日本嗰張圖<br />\n都係得<br />\n<br />\n反警暴<br />\n反種族歧視<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個係普世價值<br />\n咁點解唔用嚟CONNECT全世界呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家驚BLM係太敏感<br />\n或者令到唔知左膠/奶共政客唔鍾意<br />\n咁All Lives Matter一定啱咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c010d264aa66344c0dd3b4d0e8598e0eea238b","tid":2048482,"uid":29476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ab1d22fed9ba3bfab806f2735a108787eae052","tid":2048482,"uid":301880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:58:35.000Z","msg":"其實大家睇睇日本嗰張圖<br />\n都係得<br />\n<br />\n反警暴<br />\n反種族歧視<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個係普世價值<br />\n咁點解唔用嚟CONNECT全世界呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家驚BLM係太敏感<br />\n或者令到唔知左膠/奶共政客唔鍾意<br />\n咁All Lives Matter一定啱咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"其實都唔係 <br />\n我同你講<br />\n呢個世界真係乜都有人屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0As9Xv4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0As9Xv4.png&h=cbe0b7a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9f030604f65bc29cae47b92d9183c8179b423a7","tid":2048482,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"五毛叫兒登狗唔好理美國示威 唔好表態 兒登狗又信晒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2047402\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2047402</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d66c18e37a186489d564ce04ad49199df244f96","tid":2048482,"uid":43724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:14:03.000Z","msg":"同意如果近期有個遊行可以高舉 &quot;All Lives Matter, Black Lives Matter, HK Lives Also Matter&quot;   可能全世界都會幫香港<br />\n一齊反警暴  順便可以帶出黎比全世界仲未知既人睇"},{"pid":"3677759c443f3019c602cec7efcb9b33946e79e5","tid":2048482,"uid":301880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f7c010d264aa66344c0dd3b4d0e8598e0eea238b","tid":2048482,"uid":29476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ab1d22fed9ba3bfab806f2735a108787eae052","tid":2048482,"uid":301880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:58:35.000Z","msg":"其實大家睇睇日本嗰張圖<br />\n都係得<br />\n<br />\n反警暴<br />\n反種族歧視<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個係普世價值<br />\n咁點解唔用嚟CONNECT全世界呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家驚BLM係太敏感<br />\n或者令到唔知左膠/奶共政客唔鍾意<br />\n咁All Lives Matter一定啱咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"其實都唔係 <br />\n我同你講<br />\n呢個世界真係乜都有人屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0As9Xv4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0As9Xv4.png&h=cbe0b7a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:29:34.000Z","msg":"其實佢LOGIC有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. ALM係一個價值觀，但係佢用一個生活實例嚟做例子就唔合理<br />\n根據佢嘅邏輯<br />\n係唔係冇人犯法就唔洗有制定法律？<br />\n係唔係冇人偷嘢屋企就唔洗鎖門？<br />\n係唔係冇人用到你部電話就唔洗SET密碼？<br />\n<br />\n2. 全世界都有種族歧視<br />\n有邊一個多於一個種族存在嘅國定係冇？"},{"pid":"f804f0b9b54bd9bf4177b565bd3615f3f501f033","tid":2048482,"uid":29476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvihnFN.